<% @title="Home" %>
<% @description="The UF BCM exists to help students at the University of Florida come to know Jesus Christ in a personal way. The Baptist Collegiate Ministries care about students and care about Christ." %>
<div id="carousel-example" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
  <div class="carousel-overlay"></div>

<!--Images in the carousel should be 6000x2700 pixels-->
<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
  <!-- Indicators -->
  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1" class=""></li>
    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2" class=""></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="carousel-inner fullheight" role="listbox">
    <div class="item active">
      <%= image_tag("1.jpg", alt: "UF Baptist Collegiate Ministries") %>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1>Baptist Collegiate Ministries</h1>
          <p>The UF BCM exists to connect students to a relationship with Christ.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <%= image_tag("2.jpg", alt: "Gator is our weekly worship service every Tuesday at 8:00") %>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1>Join Us For Gator</h1>
          <p>Gator is our weekly worship service in our building every Tuesday at 8:00.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <%= image_tag("3.jpg", alt: "Join a Bible Study or volunteer with the UF BCM") %>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1>Get Involved</h1>
          <p>We have all sorts of Bible studies and volunteer opportunities to get involved in! Contact us for more info.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </a>
  <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </a>
</div>

<div class="main-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-4 icon-row">
        <div class="glyphicon-ring">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-book glyphicon-bordered"></span>
        </div>
        <p style="padding-top:10px;">The BCM offers many opportunities for students to get involved in connection groups. These groups are for all ages and are a great way to really connect to peers, connect to the community, and connect to Christ.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 icon-row">
        <div class="glyphicon-ring">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home glyphicon-bordered"></span>
        </div>
        <p style="padding-top:10px;">The BCM partners with local churches in order to help students get connected. By finding a church home, students get the chance to connect with brothers and sisters in Christ of all ages, allowing them to grow in their relationships with Christ.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 icon-row">
        <div class="glyphicon-ring">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-globe glyphicon-bordered"></span>
        </div>
        <p style="padding-top:10px;">The BCM cares deeply about helping others get to know Christ. This includes service projects around the community, setting up Gospel appointments with friends, and global mission trips.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
<br><br><br><br>
